import React from 'react'
import { Typography, Box, createTheme, ThemeProvider, CssBaseline, Link } from '@mui/material'
import VideoPlayer from './components/VideoPlayer'
import Introduction from './components/Introduction'

const customTheme = createTheme({
  root: {
    fontFamily: 'sans-serif'
  },
  palette: {
    background: {
      default: '#CDA169'
    },
    text: {
      primary: '#FFFFFF'
    }
  }
})

const App = () => {
  return (
    <ThemeProvider theme={customTheme}>
      <CssBaseline />
      <Box display='flex' flexDirection='column' justifyContent='center' alignItems='center' minHeight='100vh'>
        <Typography variant='h1'>LuomuLuola</Typography>
        <Typography variant='h2'>Liity luomuostoksille!</Typography>
        <VideoPlayer />
        <Introduction />

        <Box
          display='flex'
          flexDirection='column'
          justifyContent='center'
          alignItems='center'
          sx={{ marginTop: 'auto' }}
        >
          <Typography variant='h3'>Esittelyvideon musiikki ja logomateriaali</Typography>
          <Link
            color='inherit'
            href='https://pixabay.com/music/corporate-wake-up-to-the-renaissance-135540/'
            title='background music'
          >
            'Wake up to the renaissance' – Luonut Denys Kyshchuk (AudioCoffee) – Pixabay
          </Link>
          <Link color='inherit' href='https://www.flaticon.com/free-icons/cave' title='cave icons'>
            Luolaikoni – Luonut Freepik – Flaticon
          </Link>
          <Link color='inherit' href='https://www.flaticon.com/free-icons/seedling' title='seedling icons'>
            Kasvi-ikoni – Luonut Umeicon – Flaticon
          </Link>
        </Box>
      </Box>
    </ThemeProvider>
  )
}

export default App
